                </div>
                <div class="texttt">
                    <h1>&nbsp;DRINK ATLEAST 2.5 LITRES OF WATER EVERYDAY</h1>
                    <t style="color:grey"> &nbsp; Due to insufficient intake of water, your metabolism will decrease,
                        your gut health will
                        be compromised and &nbsp;&nbsp;you will gain weight instead of losing it.
                        Less fluid in
                        the
                        body will
                        also make you feel constipated and you &nbsp;&nbsp;might face
                        difficulty
                        in
                        passing the bowel. If
                        your internal system is not working properly then weight loss is &nbsp;&nbsp;impossible.</t>
                </div>
            </div>
            <br> <br>
